Description: ====================
        cmsplugin-plain-text
        ====================
        
        |pypi| |ci|
        
        .. |pypi| image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/cmsplugin-plain-text.png
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/cmsplugin-plain-text
